Quel est la variation du Ca entre 2 mois consécutifs en 2025
Quel est la variation du Ca entre 2 mois consécutifs en 2025

-- Requête SQL envoyée :

WITH MonthlyCA AS (
    SELECT
        year,
        month,
        SUM(ca_recharges) AS monthly_ca
    FROM
        reporting_ca_monthly
    WHERE
        year = 2025
    GROUP BY
        year,
        month
),
LaggedCA AS (
    SELECT
        year,
        month,
        monthly_ca,
        LAG(monthly_ca, 1, 0) OVER (ORDER BY year, month) AS previous_month_ca
    FROM
        MonthlyCA
)
SELECT
    year,
    month,
    (monthly_ca - previous_month_ca) AS ca_variation
FROM
    LaggedCA
ORDER BY
    year,
    month;

-- Requête SQL envoyée :

SELECT
    year AS year,
    month AS month,
    CASE
        WHEN nb_j_distinct = 0 THEN 'Inactif'
        WHEN nb_j_distinct BETWEEN 1 AND 7 THEN 'Occasionnel'
        WHEN nb_j_distinct BETWEEN 8 AND 20 THEN 'Régulier'
        ELSE 'Intensif'
    END AS segment,
    COUNT(DISTINCT MSISDN) AS nombre_utilisateurs
FROM
    daily_parc_illiflex
WHERE year = YEAR(CURRENT_DATE())
GROUP BY
    year,
    month,
    CASE
        WHEN nb_j_distinct = 0 THEN 'Inactif'
        WHEN nb_j_distinct BETWEEN 1 AND 7 THEN 'Occasionnel'
        WHEN nb_j_distinct BETWEEN 8 AND 20 THEN 'Régulier'
        ELSE 'Intensif'
    END
ORDER BY
    year DESC,
    month DESC,
    segment;
Déterminer la meilleure période de souscription (début mois, mi-mois fin du mois) du mois de janvier

-- Requête SQL envoyée :

SELECT
    year AS year,
    month AS month,
    CASE
        WHEN day BETWEEN (year * 10000 + month * 100 + 1) AND (year * 10000 + month * 100 + 10) THEN 'Debut mois'
        WHEN day BETWEEN (year * 10000 + month * 100 + 11) AND (year * 10000 + month * 100 + 20) THEN 'Mi-mois'
        ELSE 'Fin mois'
    END AS periode,
    SUM(sous_mnt) AS chiffre_affaire
FROM
    daily_souscription
WHERE
    month = 1
    AND year = YEAR(CURRENT_DATE())
GROUP BY
    year,
    month,
    CASE
        WHEN day BETWEEN (year * 10000 + month * 100 + 1) AND (year * 10000 + month * 100 + 10) THEN 'Debut mois'
        WHEN day BETWEEN (year * 10000 + month * 100 + 11) AND (year * 10000 + month * 100 + 20) THEN 'Mi-mois'
        ELSE 'Fin mois'
    END
ORDER BY
    chiffre_affaire DESC;
